{"tid":1163824,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[求安慰]被分手 好想合埋眼唔再起身","createTime":"2019-05-20T16:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T09:15:56.000Z","uid":174192,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e421ed9fecbc4236e035fde6683b7886626369d9","tid":1163824,"uid":174192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:19:17.000Z","msg":"講下背景先<br />\n自己一個住，屋企人搬走曬 平時少見面既<br />\n上年年尾同同居女友分左手，戴左綠帽。一齊左三年。最後佢搬走左。個段時間真係好難受<br />\n失戀 自己一個住，冇人冇乜。個段時間，真係好想自殺。糾纏左幾個月，每日係屋企，冇力氣去做任何事。好怕返屋企，好怕自己一個，無依靠。<br />\n<br />\n到最近，同六年前既女友一齊返，我好慶幸可以再續前緣，因為當初係我離開佢先。我一直好後悔。我以為我搵到我既婚姻我既依靠。殊不知，佢今日同我講分手，話唔想拍拖。前後大家先一齊左一個月。<br />\n<br />\n而家，我實在不知道如何面對呢一關。先後插兩刀。真係捱不住了。<br />\n好少開po，但實在唔知道點支持。好想唔再生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5a85e11502e74e03f59efb87e8addf88f01e9e3","tid":1163824,"uid":254259,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb4d1f3d0a460ecd006dd4ac6ac67055d61d9d78","tid":1163824,"uid":247912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:24:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fd520c52b36cfefb8429f14b87f7b585f8e8704","tid":1163824,"uid":162693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:29:50.000Z","msg":"點解會同六年前嘅女朋友一齊返"},{"pid":"b60d55542e16be4ee287e336d755ba5d8dba6d9b","tid":1163824,"uid":43051,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"辛苦你喇 如果可以不如去個長旅行啦?"},{"pid":"1fdcfbed42bcf49a8eb458575e01bc4a4be86f8e","tid":1163824,"uid":174017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,